Service Staff signs in.
Service Staff selects click on “Create Availability”.
System displays the current week calendar.
Service Staff inputs their availability on the calendar.
Service Staff submits the finalized availability.
System saves the availability and provides a confirmation message.
System sends the finalized availability to the manager.

Alternate/Exceptional Flows:
5a. If there are already 5 employees on the same shift, the system displays an error message.
5b. Service Staff chooses an alternative shift.
